original_title: Patriotic Cartoon Classics: 25 All-American Cartoons from World War II
overview: Celebrate America with 2.5 hours of classic cartoons for Victory from the war era. Characters include Bugs Bunny, Porky Pig, Daffy Duck, Popeye, Superman, Mr. Hook and Private Snafu (a character that Dr. Seuss help create).
title: Patriotic Cartoon Classics: 25 All-American Cartoons from World War II
